    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Symbol of\nService\nMESSAGE\nPOST CARD\nIN FLIGHT VIA AMERICAN AIRLINES\nADDRESS\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nPRINTED IN U.S.A.\nDOMESTIC POSTAGE 3С\nAIRMAIL POSTAGE 6C\nFOREIGN MAILING INQUIRE LOCALLY\n2015166.2577",
      "DID YOU KNOW?\nThat hot meals were first served on American\nAirlines (nee Airways) in 1932.\nThat approximately 169,789 gallons of coffee\nare consumed per year on American Airlines\nFlagships.\nThat all Flagship meals are complimentary.\nAMERICAN\nAIRLINES\nAMERICAN OVERSEAS AIRLINES, INC.\nAMERICAN AIRLINES, INC.\nDINNER MENU\nAppetizer\nCelery\nOlive\nBroiled Tenderloin Steak\nMushroom Sauce\nJuliene Green Beans Parsley Potatoes\nFlagship Salad\nHot Cloverleaf Rolls\nButter\nFresh Fruit Dessert\nCoffee\nTea\nMilk"
